9#include <openssl/crypto.h>
10
11#include "internal/tsan_assist.h"
12
13struct lhash_node_st {
14 void *data;
15 struct lhash_node_st *next;
16 unsigned long hash;
17};
18
19struct lhash_st {
20 OPENSSL_LH_NODE **b;
21 OPENSSL_LH_COMPFUNC comp;
22 OPENSSL_LH_HASHFUNC hash;
23 unsigned int num_nodes;
24 unsigned int num_alloc_nodes;
25 unsigned int p;
26 unsigned int pmax;
27 unsigned long up_load; /* load times 256 */
28 unsigned long down_load; /* load times 256 */
29 unsigned long num_items;
30 unsigned long num_expands;
31 unsigned long num_expand_reallocs;
32 unsigned long num_contracts;
33 unsigned long num_contract_reallocs;
34 TSAN_QUALIFIER unsigned long num_hash_calls;
35 TSAN_QUALIFIER unsigned long num_comp_calls;
36 unsigned long num_insert;
37 unsigned long num_replace;
38 unsigned long num_delete;
39 unsigned long num_no_delete;
40 TSAN_QUALIFIER unsigned long num_retrieve;
41 TSAN_QUALIFIER unsigned long num_retrieve_miss;
42 TSAN_QUALIFIER unsigned long num_hash_comps;
43 int error;
44};
